  "body": "<!--\r\n  Thanks for participating in this project! We will try to answer as soon as possible 🙏\r\n-->\r\n\r\n**Describe the bug 🐛**\r\n\r\nAmong other things I haven't found yet, `helper.toggleRefinement` -> `helper.toggleFacetRefinement`\r\n\r\n**To Reproduce 🔍**\r\nIn lots of places, one is in `connectMenu` for example, but it's best to do them all at once, also change the tests etc.\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior 💭**\r\nReplace all usage of deprecated helper functions, so we can remove them\r\n",
